Package: AorticPredictor
Title: Aortic Root Diameter Prediction using Clinical and Demographic Features
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: Shivansh Singh <singh19@usf.edu> [aut, cre]
Description: AorticPredictor provides a set of functions for performing simple linear
    regression using demographic and clinical features to predict aortic root 
    diameter. This package facilitates data preprocessing, model fitting, and 
    prediction, streamlining the analysis process for researchers 
    and practitioners. With intuitive functions and clear documentation, users can
    easily apply linear regression techniques to their echocardiogram datasets,
    aiding in the understanding and prediction of aortic root diameters.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
